content:
Thank you so much for the chat! I think we've covered everything, and I'm feeling inspired to incorporate some coastal chic and minimalist vibes into my (hypothetical) living room. If I have any more questions or need further assistance, I'll definitely reach out.

In the meantime, I hope you have a fantastic time shopping at World Market and Target this weekend! May you find some amazing gifts, unique decor, and adorable summer dresses.

Feel free to reach out if you need any more recommendations or just want to chat about home decor, shopping, or anything else. I'm always here to help!
